data.description: Welcome to your slice of paradise! Beautifully renovated waterfront home with NEW ROOF as of May 2021. No fixed bridges, bring your boat and enjoy 45ft of dockage. This spacious two story, 4 bedroom, 3 bath home offers incredible natural light and an open floor plan which make it ideal for working and living in paradise! Minutes from the beach, shopping and restaurants and major highways.  High impact windows and doors, stainless steel appliances, built in audio system & surround sound, 2 central A/C units, and an extra-large one car garage. This home is a must see!
